  "keyFeatures": [
    "Read, write, and manipulate Excel 2007+ .xlsx and .xlsm files without Excel installed",
    "Intuitive fluent API for workbooks, worksheets, cells, and ranges",
    "Full support for cell styles: fonts, borders, fills, number formats",
    "Tables with sorting, filtering, totals rows, and structured references",
    "Pivot tables with caching and data summarization",
    "AutoFilter with custom filter conditions and sorting",
    "Formula evaluation with 400+ supported Excel functions",
    "Bulk data insertion from IEnumerable, DataTable, and other sources",
    "Workbook and worksheet protection with password support",
    "Conditional formatting, sparklines, charts, and drawings",
    ".NET Standard 2.0 library — runs on .NET Core, .NET Framework, and Blazor"
  ],
